<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_97_r1l10"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als vns eẅr gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der angrıff <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l11">dıe vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beſchehen ſınd Jn dem lande ʒu Beheim von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l12"><expan>Frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofſteın . vnd Nıclas <expan>lang<ex>en</ex></expan> . vvıe eẅch <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l13">daʒ wır eẅch darinn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>denken</expan> etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l14">Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kawffleẅt vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe dıe ſache antrıft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l15">für vns beſant vnd mıt Jn dauon gerett / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſeıd dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l16">mal . vns denn eẅr gnade ſchreıbt / daʒ Jr mıt <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>angrıff<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l17">niht Handels noch ʒe <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd auch <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> teıl noch gemein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l18">daran habt das ıſt vns lıeb . vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch eẅr gnade des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l19"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>wıſſen</expan> . Denn als vns eẅr gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l20">ſıchern VVıſſen wır niht vvelch <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſein <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wıe </ab>
